cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on the development of a counterfeit goods detection platform that uses a convolutional neural network (CNN) for image analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other possible sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), as the paper also deals with the problem of counterfeit goods trade and the development of a reliable solution for it, which involves aspects of security, machine learning, and information retrieval.
